{"tid":1421653,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"LEARN from Enemy：向狗狗學習記者會發言技巧","createTime":"2019-08-06T08:34:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T10:14:24.000Z","uid":260529,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"81a15a39d06f2d6da59cacb6ea15b022591255df","tid":1421653,"uid":260529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:34:38.000Z","msg":"隨住今次運動<strong>曠日持久</strong>，同時<strong>人vs狗記者會</strong>戰線開啟，我地都要學識點打民意戰，<span style=\"color: red;\">點做好啲PR</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>狗狗記者會開場發言妓巧：</ins></strong><br />\n- 不斷以<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>暴徒</strong></span>稱呼示威者，企圖<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>潛移默化</strong></span><br />\n- 宏觀以至微觀地<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>總結</strong></span>前線對佢地造成嘅<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>破壞</strong></span>，並有<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>數字支持</strong></span><br />\n- 嘗試論證示威者嘅行動<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>如何對平民造成影響</strong></span>（意圖拉攏民意）<br />\n- 之後先講射左幾多彈等等，緊接住又講返啲狗受左傷<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>好慘慘豬</strong></span>啊<br />\n<br />\n學野時間：<br />\n1. 我地應該搵一個點既稱呼，可以言簡意賅地令市民知道佢地既不堪？<br />\n2. 要有手足總結每日<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">狗狗做過既暴行</span></strong>，並喺記者會上清晰展示<br />\n3. 要重點提<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">狗狗發癲點影響平民生活</span></strong><br />\n4. Highlight示威者所受傷害，同時情感上令大眾同情示威者<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">！！光復香港，時代革命！！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"584459f9d38a5b8a95de0773437831848d485a32","tid":1421653,"uid":153186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:36:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"45fff18b97387a692b2ffa3db2c6ce57cb400a39","tid":1421653,"uid":260793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:38:55.000Z","msg":"Push!!!"},{"pid":"8d9fe016e98c986574988ea06688e9f0ca63e27a","tid":1421653,"uid":224642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-